      <listitem>
       <para>
        <xref linkend="cha.tuning.memory.vm.writeback"/>: Important
        difference in timing of I/O writes in SLE 12
        (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=907504"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
     </itemizedlist>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
 </sect1>
 <sect1 xml:id="sec.tuning.docupdates.sle12_ga">
  <title>October 2014 (Initial Release of &productname; 12)</title>

  <!--list of general issues that apply to all books-->
  <xi:include href="common_docupdates_ga_i.xml"/>

  <variablelist>
   <varlistentry>
<!-- 2 System Monitoring Utilities -->
    <term><xref linkend="cha.util"/>
    </term>
    <listitem>
     <itemizedlist mark="bullet" spacing="normal">
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Updated command outputs with samples produced with &sle; 12.
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Corrected the description of <literal>si</literal>,
        <literal>so</literal> and <literal>in</literal> in
        <xref linkend="sec.util.multi.vmstat"/>.
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Corrected the explanation for <literal>majflt</literal> and
        the statement about spreading I/O requests over multiple disks in
        <xref linkend="sec.util.multi.sar.report"/>.
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Replaced deprecated tools <command>ifconfig</command> and
        <command>netstat</command> with <command>ip</command>,
        <command>ethtool</command> and <command>ss</command> in
        <xref linkend="sec.util.networking"/>.
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Added documentation about <command>sysctl</command> to
        <xref linkend="sec.util.proc.procinfo.sysctl"/>.
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Added the section <xref linkend="sec.util.hardware.mcelog"/>.
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Added details on <command>/usr/bin/time</command> to
        <xref linkend="sec.util.time.time"/>.
       </para>
      </listitem>
     </itemizedlist>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   <varlistentry>
<!-- 4 SystemTapâ€”Filtering and Analyzing System Data -->
    <term><xref linkend="cha.tuning.systemtap"/>
    </term>
    <listitem>
     <para>
      Added a link to the example scripts Web page to
      <xref linkend="sec.tuning.systemtap.concept.scripts"/>.
     </para>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   <varlistentry>
    <term><xref linkend="cha.tuning.oprofile"/>
    </term>
    <listitem>
     <para>
      Corrected statements on the effects of sampling rates in
      <xref linkend="sec.tuning.oprofile.events"/>.
     </para>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   <varlistentry>
<!-- 9 Automatic Non-Uniform Memory Access (NUMA) Balancing -->
    <term><xref linkend="cha.tuning.numactl"/>
    </term>
    <listitem>
     <para>
      New chapter.
     </para>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   <varlistentry>
<!-- 12 Tuning the Task Scheduler -->
    <term><xref linkend="cha.tuning.taskscheduler"/>
    </term>
    <listitem>
     <itemizedlist mark="bullet" spacing="normal">
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Removed section about the outdated <literal>O1</literal> task
        scheduler.
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Clarified kernel variables in
        <xref linkend="cha.tuning.memory.usage.writeback"/>.
       </para>
      </listitem>
     </itemizedlist>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   <varlistentry>
<!-- 13 Tuning the Memory Management Subsystem -->
    <term><xref linkend="cha.tuning.memory"/>
    </term>
    <listitem>
     <para>
      Added detailed descriptions on tunable parameters to
      <xref linkend="cha.tuning.memory.vm.writeback"/>.
     </para>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   <varlistentry>
<!-- 16 Kexec and Kdump -->
    <term><xref linkend="cha.tuning.kexec"/>
    </term>
    <listitem>
     <itemizedlist mark="bullet" spacing="normal">
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Added a tip on sharing the dump directory in
        <xref linkend="cha.tuning.kdump.basic.yast"/> (Fate #313185).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Added a tip on identifying a kernel crash dump with
        <command>kdumpid</command> (Fate #312855) to
        <xref linkend="cha.tuning.kdump.analyze"/>.
       </para>
      </listitem>
     </itemizedlist>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   <varlistentry>
    <term>Obsolete Content</term>
    <listitem>
     <itemizedlist mark="bullet" spacing="normal">
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Chapter <citetitle>Monitoring with Nagios</citetitle> has been
        removed from <xref linkend="part.tuning.monitoring"/> (Fate
        #316136), because Nagios is no longer shipped on &sle; 12.
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Chapter <citetitle>Perf mon2&mdash;Hardware-Based Performance
        Monitoring</citetitle> has been removed from
        <xref linkend="part.tuning.kerneltrace"/>, because perfmon2 is no
        longer shipped on &sle; 12.
       </para>
      </listitem>
     </itemizedlist>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   <varlistentry>
    <term>Bugfixes</term>
    <listitem>
     <itemizedlist mark="bullet" spacing="normal">
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Removed notes about <literal>zone_reclaim_mode</literal> in
        <xref linkend="cha.tuning.memory"/>
        (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=874971"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
     </itemizedlist>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
